<span id="freeTextContainer7030335742863480775">Someone asked me why I had so many different copies of Neruda and I answered because no one book ever has all the poems or the translations that I want. That&apos;s the tricky thing about Neruda. It&apos;s also the reason I like dual translation editions, so I can see the original right next to the English. </span>
  <span id="freeText7030335742863480775" style="display:none">Someone asked me why I had so many different copies of Neruda and I answered because no one book ever has all the poems or the translations that I want. That's the tricky thing about Neruda. It's also the reason I like dual translation editions, so I can see the original right next to the English. </span>
  <a data-text-id="7030335742863480775" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

